{"tid":2397299,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"北約籲全球民主國同抗中","createTime":"2021-02-06T10:02:44.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-06T14:45:04.000Z","uid":25558,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"25d728b5c92833dcedd8ccd77afcf9bd3dab7172","tid":2397299,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T10:02:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210206/AGGW6HNCCZHF7NOF6T2LQETLSA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210206%2FAGGW6HNCCZHF7NOF6T2LQETLSA%2F&d=ZxGTC5m4wH5D2fXTYNKMIaF0%2BEjl5hukozrtPJpxOa8%3D&h=8b6ebe88\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210206%2FAGGW6HNCCZHF7NOF6T2LQETLSA%2F&h=b9ad37e4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210206/AGGW6HNCCZHF7NOF6T2LQETLSA/</a><br />\n<br />\n北約籲全球民主國同抗中<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Z8EDRMM4OYF68M01uMJVSiktIwk=/887x591/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/XB75C7IH2RDHPP24U6X5U5DFIU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FZ8EDRMM4OYF68M01uMJVSiktIwk%3D%2F887x591%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FXB75C7IH2RDHPP24U6X5U5DFIU.jpg&h=9ce3875e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n北約秘書長斯托爾滕貝格（Jens Stoltenberg）表示，北約必須「放眼全球」，與全球民主國家建立新的夥伴關係，以抗衡中國越來越大的挑戰，呼應美國總統拜登的說法。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：首外交演說 強調修復盟國關係  拜登宣告美國回來 「華是最難纏競爭者」<br />\n<br />\n斯托爾滕貝格前天向英國皇家國際事務研究所發表的視像講話，是美國大選後他首次發表政策演說，當中他點名指中國和俄羅斯對北約有潛在技術威脅，成員國軍隊必須對兩國發展的干擾性技術領先一步，並強調成員國的基建和供應線，不應依賴觀念不同的國家。<br />\n<br />\n他又表示，雖然北約應該維持。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：推翻特朗普與華脫鈎政策<br />\n<br />\n斯托爾滕貝格的說法，呼應了拜登和英國首相約翰遜的民主十國集團（D10）構思。兩人想在6月的七國集團（G7）峯會，討論在G7加入印韓澳結成新聯盟。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n美駐聯大使曾撐華受質疑<br />\n<br />\n另外，拜登提名的駐聯合國大使人選托。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n英國《泰晤士報》"},{"pid":"ca55ee50134f294703262e50e1d72b7be1e5991c","tid":2397299,"uid":296410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T14:30:21.000Z","msg":"有乜行動先"},{"pid":"32fd6517f51657c304b2cc89aae6140bdebdc2b8","tid":2397299,"uid":44646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T14:45:04.000Z","msg":"張相唔係斯托爾滕貝格"}]}